  <ul>
    <li>Use the search box, or browse using the terms on the left side to discover content.</li>
    <li>Some content is only available when you <% link_to '', 'sign in' %> with your ID and passphrase.</li>
    <li>Login to <a href="https://oncourse.iu.edu">Oncourse</a> or <a href="https://canvas.iu.edu">Canvas</a> to access course materials.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
<div id="home-visit-box" class="span3">
  <p>Visit <a href="http://wiki.dlib.indiana.edu/display/MCO">Media Collections Online</a> services web site to learn about services for IU units.</p>
</div>
</div>
